#

Beef Wellington with Garlic Mashed Potatoes

$45
700 kcal
Difficulty: 80%

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

Main CourseElegantComfort Food

Description

A classic dish that combines tender beef fillet with a rich mushroom duxelles, all wrapped in golden pastry and served with creamy garlic mashed potatoes.

Ingredients

  • Beef tenderloin: 2 lbs
  • Puff pastry: 1 sheet
  • Mushrooms: 10 oz
  • Prosciutto: 6 slices
  • Dijon mustard: 2 tbsp
  • Egg yolk: 1
  • Garlic: 4 cloves
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • Potatoes: 2 lbs
  • Fresh thyme: 2 sprigs
